data.description: Corner lot diamond in the rough ready for your personal touch. Located in Calallen ISD this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home boasts walk-in closets, vaulted ceilings, wood burning fireplace and two car garage with tons of storage. The bright and open concept living-room/dining-room is perfect for entertaining. Enjoy your evenings on the extended patio in shaded backyard complete with dog run. The oversized driveway lends itself for multiple vehicles, boat, or RV. This one-of-a-kind single story home is walking distance to neighborhood parks, Oil Belt Little League, and located only minutes from grocery stores and dining options. Don't wait and make your appointment to tour today!
